Manage Branch Information
Description:
The Manage Branch Information module allows administrators to create, view, update, and delete branch records within the Inventory Management System. It stores essential information about each business branch, such as the branch name, address, contact details, manager, and operating status. This module helps businesses organize operations across multiple locations and maintain accurate branch information.
Features
Add a new branch
View branch details
Edit branch information
Delete inactive branches
Search and filter branches
Manage branch contact information
Assign a branch manager
Enable or disable branch status
User Story
As an administrator, I want to manage branch information so that I can keep accurate records of all business branches and efficiently organize inventory operations across different locations.
